{
  "stem": "4187.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, yeah, we were truly a-- a-- a praying family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and often-- my father never came to church with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I often saw him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, he'd be standing at another-- another-- when I say, often, not-- not every week.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, they probably, my-- with my mother, they went elsewhere and to another church.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A great number of times, I saw him in church.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- Was there antisemitism in the school or in the community?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was antisemitism, but this-- this is a very peculiar-- I-- I have very mixed memories with this, because, for a long time, I wasn't at the receiving end.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although, there were two Jewish girls in-- in my class, and we were very friendly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they weren't-- so there was antisemitism, but it wasn't turned on these two girls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were both-- mind you, I don't know exactly where they were invited.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were certainly invited to our place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But whether they were as much in with the others, I'm afraid I wouldn't like to say, because I just can't remember.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the antisemitism wasn't such, at that stage, that one would have said, what's happening here?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you know what was-- what-- what did happen to us, and especially to me, because I had a very Jewish nose, which is now-- well, has been operated.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, it's been sliced a long time ago.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Anyway, we-- in the street, we'd be called dirty Jews, filthy Jews, stinking Jews, you know whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And often, we'd say to my mother, what on Earth are these people talking about?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she said, you-- you have-- you look Italian, which was true, my-- especially my sister looked very Italian-ish, because my father looked Italian-- well, half-Italian.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
